    <section address="Starting">
      <title>Starting</title>
      <content>
        <para>After starting the <token>app</token>, on the screen appears splash screen:</para>
        <mediaLink>
          <caption placement="after" lead="Figure">Logo</caption>
          <image placement="center" xlink:href = "0c9512e4-f88f-459b-982b-b46ff063ed29"/>
        </mediaLink>
        <para>Then appears the main window:</para>
        <mediaLink>
          <caption placement="after" lead="Figure">Main window</caption>
          <image placement="center" xlink:href = "69068e75-3086-4c33-b054-4ffcc92be6ab"/>
        </mediaLink>
        <para>Controls in the main window:</para>
        <list class="ordered">
          <listItem>
            <para>
              TreeView panel, where all <token>SHFB</token> project elements are shown
            </para>
          </listItem>
          <listItem>
            <para>
              Information panel, where information about help element (image, code entity, external link, token, topic) are shown.
            </para>
          </listItem>
          <listItem>
            <para>
              Checkbox (FormattedLink), if the box is checked, the link will be in formatted form.
            </para>
          </listItem>
          <listItem>
            <para>
              Menu bar with “File” menu and “Help” menu.
            </para>
          </listItem>
          <listItem>
            <para>
              External link panel, where external links can be created.
            </para>
          </listItem>
        </list>  
      </content>
